Second Department,

November, 1938.

(November 4, 1938.) George L. Albert, Appellant, v. Jerome Fiske Collins, Respondent.

Motion for reargument denied, with ten dollars costs. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Motion for a stay denied. Present' — Lazansky, P. J., Hagarty, Davis, Adel and Taylor, JJ.
